{"tid":1664169,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《NBA籃網賽場內 百名反送支挺港觀眾著黑衣現身》","createTime":"2019-10-20T02:21:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T16:52:06.000Z","uid":32511,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"37461ae29efd75eea8b72d859412c00770cfa6a8","tid":1664169,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T02:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f3193uy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff3193uy.jpg&h=cd56cb4e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AxLCsWe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAxLCsWe.jpg&h=807a34d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3BRxnW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3BRxnW.jpg&h=ce982168&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mS3wxnX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmS3wxnX.jpg&h=998bc4b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bwgqBPD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbwgqBPD.jpg&h=d926d7c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國職籃NBA推特風波仍未平息。上百名聲援香港反送中示威活動的民眾，今晚身著「和香港站在一起」的黑色T恤現身紐約布魯克林籃網（Nets）賽事，支持香港示威運動。<br />\n <br />\n國會山莊報（The Hill）引述紐約雜誌（New York Magazine）與哈芬登郵報（HuffPost）撰稿記者阿里（Yashar Ali）的推特指出，這項活動是由製作人兼社運人士鄧肯（Andrew Duncan）贊助。<br />\n <br />\n根據阿里的推文，鄧肯購買300張門票，讓示威者得以前往籃網今晚在紐約布魯克林主場與多倫多暴龍隊（Toronto Raptors）的比賽。<br />\n <br />\n從照片中可以看到許多身穿「和香港站在一起」（Stand With Hong Kong）黑色T恤的抗議者也戴著黑色口罩，表達對香港運動的支持。香港眾志常委羅冠聰也現身場內。<br />\n <br />\nNBA休士頓火箭總經理摩瑞4日在社群媒體推特（Twitter）發文力挺香港民主抗爭，掀起風波。面對中國揚言抵制，NBA總裁席佛（Adam Silver）捍衛言論自由，堅決不道歉，他並透露，中國政府要求開除摩瑞，「我們說那不可能發生，甚至連處罰他都不可能」。<br />\n <br />\n相較於席佛堅持捍衛言論自由立場，台灣出生的籃網隊新老闆蔡崇信在臉書個人專頁上，發表致所有NBA球迷的公開信。他寫道，「西方媒體和對中國持批判態度的人，嚴重誤解及經常忽略的一件事情，就是論及中國領土完整和國家主權問題時，14億中國人會團結一致。這項議題沒有商討餘地」。<br />\n <br />\n蔡崇信的發言讓他遭評立場親北京。他之後接受「華爾街日報」（Wall Street Journal）訪問時表示，他的發言用意是讓讀者理解，英國與日本等國前幾世紀曾入侵並占據中國領土，這段歷史讓中國人面對分離主義運動議題時產生強烈屈辱與憤怒感。他也感嘆，自己只想扮演和事佬，希望風波盡快平息。"},{"pid":"782c3d5c59397a87f51660636a743d4491e779a4","tid":1664169,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee7114c6df5cec7f156033fc2cd189c91157aff","tid":1664169,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:32:24.000Z","msg":"抵死，全球反支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bef058036964766e66f3a9871905b26e18165e8","tid":1664169,"uid":30145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:36:32.000Z","msg":"&quot;新疆&rdquo;及&ldquo;西藏&rdquo;等地前幾世紀曾遭入侵並占據領土，這段歷史讓當地人面對中國統一議題時產生強烈屈辱與憤怒感。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2d9f295a56b5f10d0166d410061af132ff3666","tid":1664169,"uid":64744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:38:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"015c88827b169339c499a930e7600c1bc24759ef","tid":1664169,"uid":275175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:58:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34316e5ed347ccb08af42da68057ee4ae1306b77","tid":1664169,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:35:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11d287fe8440cff606209b953b9a5045b4baca10","tid":1664169,"uid":176996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:10:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"845eea3910c844e0d63fad8cfce1c8e2e8f79be4","tid":1664169,"uid":276989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}